{"tid":648164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個呀叔問我揀邊隻安全套好","createTime":"2018-04-30T12:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T17:16:13.000Z","uid":42058,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"27773477251eee6eb1a253726357ad2cbb31fb60","tid":648164,"uid":42058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:31:27.000Z","msg":"番緊便利店，今日有個呀叔走過黎問我安全套點賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :呀叔<br />\n<br />\n呀叔:喂 細路 呢到有無安全套賣 <br />\n我:有啊 係COUNTER下面 你可以睇下 <br />\n呀叔:哇 咁多隻 咁你知唔知邊款好用 <br />\n我心諗:我青頭仔鬼撚識分咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我當然無咁講啦<br />\n我:杜記同肛本 都幾多人買架 <br />\n跟住佢一盒一盒咁拎哂上黎問我價錢<br />\n仆街等陣又要我擺番哂落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀叔:喂 呢隻0.03 同 0.01 有咩分別 <br />\n我:係厚薄既分別<br />\n呀叔:下 0.03 咪好撚薄 咁撚唔安全既 <br />\n呀叔:我要厚D既有無 咁撚薄 咪好撚易穿 會出事 <br />\n仆你個街 成間野全部都係0.01 0.03 咁賣架啦 D客仔全部買呢D架啦 要厚既帶2個呀笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:唔好意思呀先生 呢到都係得呢D咁薄既賣 其實好多客仔都買呢D 應該無問題既<br />\n呀叔:你識唔識架? 睇你個樣 安全套都未撚用過啦 <br />\n我:屌閪你就叻 揀安全套又唔見你咁撚叻?<br />\n講完呢句之後我地互相對望 靜左幾秒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家佢閪都唔撚屌同緊我經理傾計 <br />\n求救 有無巴打可以救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊隻安全套係最安全最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab288089e0fe3dbb5b8fa1cace5d4aa701695f8","tid":648164,"uid":42058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /